Added a test module to the `stacks-codec` crate. Pure-codec roundtrip and corruption tests for transaction payloads, post-conditions, asset info, microblock-poison, Nakamoto coinbase, and `StacksString` were relocated from `stackslib`; new tests cover previously-untested wire-format boundaries, including byte-value pins for the enum discriminants (`TransactionPayloadID`, `TransactionAnchorMode`, `TransactionPostConditionMode`, `TransactionVersion`, `TransactionAuthFlags`, `AssetInfoID`, `PostConditionPrincipalID`), all `TenureChangeCause` variants, fixed-size assertions for `TokenTransferMemo` and `CoinbasePayload`, standalone `StacksMicroblockHeader` and `TenureChangePayload` roundtrips, and the `StacksString` printable-ASCII boundaries.
